}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== Flash chip looks like a MX25L1605
The included power adapter is a '''DVE''' DSA-12PFE-12 BUS 120100 (12V, 1A).
The default SSID follows the pattern of '''belkin.XXX''' where '''XXX''' is the last three hex digits of the WLAN MAC (lower case letters).
